## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and studies, which may not cover all aspects of how music influences mood and behavior. Additionally, cultural differences in music perception and the subjective nature of music's impact on individuals were not extensively explored. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these nuances.

